articles.title: AC Milan - Hernandez : "Ibrahimovic m'a grondé parce que j'étais en surpoids" - Goal.com
articles.description: Manchester United manager Ole Gunnar Solskjaer insists he does not feel sorry for David Moyes' woes at Old Trafford and has nothing but respect for his work with West Ham United this season.
